{"tid":544212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反對增加大學學位","createTime":"2018-01-29T09:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T12:13:52.000Z","uid":105018,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f528c967d0af2ce3061af3d32926ac32376aa1","tid":544212,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T09:48:41.000Z","msg":"成日有啲讀唔成書既人話增加大學學位<br />\n恆管又想升格<br />\n我真係心諗屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本依家香港咁細一個地方有8間大學就已經夠嗮<br />\n用下腦都知當demand冇增加到 而supply不斷增加既時候 price就會下跌<br />\n依家三大搵工都咁難 仲增加學位真係攬炒&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪想學台灣咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e36704c8da9383a91661c2047d6ebc4b6608e7","tid":544212,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"1981年，大學學位就只能滿足2%的適齡青年。根據1978年的白皮書，往後10年的高等教育學位每年只能維持3%的增長，進度非常緩慢。到80年代中期，港府在其財政預算中透露，將逐年增加大學入學率，並在2000年達到14.5%。1988年，港督衛奕信突然在其施政報告中宣布加快高等教育的步伐，把14.5%目標提前到1994年，2000年則定為18%。1989年六四事件後，港府再度加快步伐，宣布把2000年18%的目標提前到1994年實現。當年的入學率只有6%，換句話說就是要在5年內把入學率提升3倍。"},{"pid":"38bef8c26431527a9a51660781b787279d621039","tid":544212,"uid":8531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"香港非三大都唔叫真正大學生，如果恆管升格真影衰哂大學生依個身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef10d41b55dcb300d02e0b2fc61c48b03350145","tid":544212,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38bef8c26431527a9a51660781b787279d621039","tid":544212,"uid":8531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"香港非三大都唔叫真正大學生，如果恆管升格真影衰哂大學生依個身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"如果恆管 珠海都升格 最慘係非三大果班學生 冇啦啦多左咁多競爭 分分鐘出黎做野做爛市"},{"pid":"841c62c596b27d663babb0f682e6f125f2a68a76","tid":544212,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"三大搵工都難啦，屌鳩佢，而家個問題唔係凈係得local U，仲有外國U呢<br />\n<br />\n將D唔應該成為大學既學校夾硬升做大學，我睇都幾大獲"},{"pid":"c46b002d7263698852da2d425bb372f3334e7b61","tid":544212,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"841c62c596b27d663babb0f682e6f125f2a68a76","tid":544212,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"三大搵工都難啦，屌鳩佢，而家個問題唔係凈係得local U，仲有外國U呢<br />\n<br />\n將D唔應該成為大學既學校夾硬升做大學，我睇都幾大獲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"屌 諗起都sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報grad job大把大陸人同海歸一齊爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲人以為入到大學就得<br />\n其實唔係讀書既材料就做其它野啦<br />\n就算俾佢入到啲三流大學grad完咪又係搵唔到野做 仲要拖低埋大學生人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761517ec6f1ec21331e27d59af4df69201ba80f6","tid":544212,"uid":36049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"應該扣到得返4~5間先岩<br />\n個個讀完垃圾ff 自己係人才然後就埋怨自己懷才不遇"},{"pid":"974021aa6d6649d63be5e8de9c7da2ee86bdfb70","tid":544212,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761517ec6f1ec21331e27d59af4df69201ba80f6","tid":544212,"uid":36049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"應該扣到得返4~5間先岩<br />\n個個讀完垃圾ff 自己係人才然後就埋怨自己懷才不遇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"ied lingu ou<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}